com.iota.iri.utils.collections.interfaces

Interface UnIterableMap<K,V>

  • Type Parameters:
    K - The key type
    V - The value type
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    TransformingMap

    public interface UnIterableMap<K,V>
    Similar to Map but hides key retrieval functionality. Thus one can't iterate over key or entries. Implementing class may transform keys to perform memory operations
